                            <comment id="14138440" author="wanchang" created="Thu, 18 Sep 2014 03:15:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I use DummyTxnManager as the default value of hive.txn.manager. I noticed that the CREATE TEMPORARY FUNCTION requires a EXCLUSIVE lock while it&apos;s writetype is DLL_NO_LOCK in the DummyTxnManager. Maybe it&apos;s a good idea to check the DLL&apos;s writetype in DummyTxnManager too.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
